AUDIO: 'hyperrealistic human flesh showing intense frustration and grit. The right side of the face is carved from cracked white marble resembling a Roman statue of Marcus Aurelius and symbolizing stoic calm. Dark moody background, cinematic lighting, golden teal color grading, 8K'

