[03:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'persona? It\'s basically a model that\'s trained on your face so pixels can add you into thumbnails or replace other faces with yours. To set one up, find personas under account on the sidebar. Click create, write your name or whatever you want to call your persona,'

[03:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and then upload at least 10 images. Though I always recommend going for around 20 because the more images you provide, the better the results will be. Once you\'re done, click generate, wait a moment, and it\'ll show up here. So, let\'s try a prompt with it. I\'ll use'

